            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1680079304128-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add your<strong> balsamic sun-dried tomato paste </strong>and your <strong>dried oregano </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> with 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cook for 4-5 min or until the sauce begins to thicken to a gravy-like consistency – this is your <strong>sun-dried tomato sauce</strong></p>",
